 157.1237, 157.7744, 155.3025, 156.0104, 155.7352, 155.5837, 154.0647, 155.1622, 156.4932, 154.8818, 155.7746, 155.7827, 155.7515, 156.5287, 156.5699, 157.0875, 157.9131, 158.732, 157.4604, 156.8843, 159.0592, 158.14, 161.4918, 163.2947, 162.9115, 162.0889, 164.0211, 164.1376, 162.5845, 160.8793, 161.4667, 162.8488, 163.2846, 157.4865, 159.5263, 162.3277, 163.9932, 167.607, 169.4494, 167.0842, 166.6544, 166.0988, 167.8054, 168.4417, 168.6339, 172.9196, 171.6872, 171.4102, 171.6089, 172.3249, 171.9069, 168.3427, 170.1207, 171.5136, 169.2345, 169.6645, 169.4445, 169.6405, 170.3675, 167.8422, 169.658, 170.7561, 170.4921, 168.042, 170.1654, 173.6001, 175.0768, 175.1307, 176.0919, 179.439, 181.9763, 179.3842, 180.3936, 182.6533, 180.2214, 182.7294, 182.1879, 182.8022, 182.1417, 184.5914, 186.3783, 186.2867, 187.7594, 187.0847, 188.2851, 187.684, 186.5993, 186.8935, 188.682, 189.1272, 189.5598, 189.4649, 189.0289, 187.5356, 188.9377, 189.509, 190.6178, 190.8087, 190.9614, 191.8939, 191.0558, 190.675, 190.4782, 189.8907, 189.5927, 189.8829, 190.2136, 190.0726, 191.0219, 191.1288, 190.8305, 191.207, 190.8128, 191.1756, 190.5446, 190.9067, 191.4455, 190.5672, 190.8083, 189.9147, 189.758, 190.8605, 189.0336, 189.7321, 190.2012, 189.7568, 190.282, 190.1704, 189.475, 190.7472, 192.5203, 193.1017, 193.024, 194.2811, 194.7014, 195.2053, 193.445, 192.7319, 192.9044, 192.5807, 192.0626, 192.0876, 192.203, 191.35], "summary_html": "<h1>商品期货的特质动量 (Idiosyncratic Momentum in Commodity Futures)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>传统的截面动量策略按过去收益排名做多赢家、做空输家。本策略的核心创新在于：先将每个品种的收益分解为系统性部分（市场、期限结构、规模因子解释的部分）和特质部分（残差），然后用特质收益的累计值替代总收益作为动量排名依据。这样做的好处是剔除了系统性因子反转带来的噪声，使动量信号更加纯净和持久。原文发现商品期货动量完全由多头组合驱动，空头组合无正贡献。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.94</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.3%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.6%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-8.8%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3434</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.97</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.9</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.51 / 1.34</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.89</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.38</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.26</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.03</span></td><td>1.16</td><td>0.78</td><td>1.41</td><td>0.3</td><td>1.2</td><td>1.23</td><td>0.63</td><td>0.8</td><td>1.28</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.94</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 231 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 231 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3436</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>87.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.3</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>总收益动量</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Mom}_{i,t} = \\frac{P_{i,t}}{P_{i,t-K}} - 1</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">K</span> 为排序期（formation period），<span class=\"math-tex\">P_{i,t}</span> 为品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 日的收盘价。</p>\n<p><strong>系统性因子回归</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">r_{i,t} = \\alpha_i + \\beta_i^{mkt} \\cdot r_t^{mkt} + \\beta_i^{ts} \\cdot r_t^{ts} + \\beta_i^{sz} \\cdot r_t^{sz} + \\varepsilon_{i,t}</div>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">r_t^{mkt}</span>: 市场因子（所有品种等权日收益均值）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">r_t^{ts}</span>: 期限结构因子（真实展期收益率 <code>ry</code> 的截面均值）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">r_t^{sz}</span>: 规模因子（OPI * 价格排名 top 33% 与 bottom 33% 日收益之差）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\beta</span> 通过 126 日滚动窗口 OLS 估计</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>特质收益动量</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\hat{\\varepsilon}_{i,t} = r_{i,t} - \\hat{\\beta}_i^{mkt} r_t^{mkt} - \\hat{\\beta}_i^{ts} r_t^{ts} - \\hat{\\beta}_i^{sz} r_t^{sz}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{IdioMom}_{i,t} = \\sum_{j=1}^{K} \\hat{\\varepsilon}_{i,t-j}</div>\n<p>截面排名后做多 top 25%，做空 bottom 25%，月度再平衡。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>所有gate通过, Sharpe 0.93 (idio_mom_ls_231d_raw)</td><td>实现全部因子：3个排序期 x (总收益+特质) x (多空+纯多头) = 12 变体</td><td>首轮即过0.8阈值。特质&gt;总收益，231d&gt;126d&gt;63d，与原文一致。</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>IC gate可优化弱品种, 换手率高(0.33)</td><td>加 sym_rolling_ic_gate + rank_to_continuous 连续仓位 + 触发 _cs/_ts 归一化</td><td>Sharpe 0.93-&gt;1.12。IC-gated + ts归一化最优。</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>已达阈值，探索189d排序期和42d持仓期</td><td>新增189d formation + 42d hold_days 网格</td><td>189d略弱于231d。42d hold与21d持平。确认231d/h21为最优。</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（59个活跃品种）。IC gate 动态过滤弱品种。</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每 21 日调仓（月度再平衡）</li>\n<li><strong>信号特点</strong>: 截面因子，需足够多品种才有区分度</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 特质收益动量需要 126 日回归窗口 + 231 日累计期 = 约 357 天热身期\n<p>- 期限结构因子使用 <code>ry</code> 字段，该字段非空率约 37%，部分品种/时段缺失 - 2016/2021/2023 年度 Sharpe 偏低（商品市场特征变化期） - 与因子库相关性 0.35（低相关，信号独立性强）</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>REG_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>126</code></td><td>rolling OLS window</td></tr><tr><td><code>FORMATION</code></td><td><code>231</code></td><td>idio momentum cumulative window</td></tr><tr><td><code>BEST_VARIANT</code></td><td><code>&quot;idio_ls_231d_gated_h21&quot;</code></td><td>base name; postprocess applies _ts</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.55s</li>\n</ul>"}